---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { pageSeo } from '../seo/page-config';

const seo = pageSeo.docs;
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-bg-primary py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <header class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">
          Task docs: install, encrypt, decrypt, verify
        </h1>
        <p class="font-body text-xl text-text-secondary max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Practical docs for current Moaiy workflows, with verification and source-build references.
        </p>
      </header>

      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-8">1. Install from official channels</h2>
        <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
          <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-4">Preferred source: official GitHub Releases.</p>
          <div class="font-code text-sm bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 overflow-x-auto mb-4">
            <div class="mb-2 text-text-tertiary"># Open official release channel</div>
            <div><span class="text-accent-primary">$</span> open https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/releases</div>
          </div>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/releases"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            data-analytics-event="download_click"
            class="inline-block px-5 py-3 bg-accent-primary text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-secondary transition-colors"
          >
            Open GitHub Releases
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <article class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">2. Generate keys</h2>
          <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-4">Create your key pair once before encryption workflows.</p>
          <div class="font-code text-sm bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 overflow-x-auto">
            <div><span class="text-accent-primary">$</span> moaiy key generate</div>
            <div class="text-text-tertiary mt-2"># Save private key securely and back it up offline.</div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">3. Encrypt data</h2>
          <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-4">Choose recipient-key mode or password mode based on your use case.</p>
          <div class="font-code text-sm bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 overflow-x-auto space-y-2">
            <div><span class="text-accent-primary">$</span> moaiy encrypt secret.txt --recipient alice@example.com</div>
            <div><span class="text-accent-primary">$</span> moaiy encrypt secret.txt --password</div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">4. Decrypt safely</h2>
          <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-4">Validate the input source and decrypt only trusted artifacts.</p>
          <div class="font-code text-sm bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 overflow-x-auto">
            <div><span class="text-accent-primary">$</span> moaiy decrypt secret.txt.gpg</div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">5. Verify artifacts</h2>
          <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-4">Always validate checksums/signatures for downloaded binaries.</p>
          <a href="/verification/" class="inline-block text-accent-primary hover:underline font-semibold">Read verification guide</a>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-16 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6">Build from source (optional)</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-4">If you prefer local builds, use the official repository:</p>
        <div class="bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg p-5 font-code text-sm text-text-secondary overflow-x-auto space-y-2">
          <div>git clone https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy.git</div>
          <div>cd moaiy</div>
          <div>open Moaiy/Moaiy.xcodeproj</div>
          <div>xcodebuild -project Moaiy/Moaiy.xcodeproj -scheme Moaiy -destination 'platform=macOS' build</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-8">Core docs links</h2>
        <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
          <ul class="font-body text-text-secondary space-y-3">
            <li>
              <a href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/blob/main/README.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-primary hover:underline">README</a>
              <span> - product overview and setup.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-primary hover:underline">CONTRIBUTING</a>
              <span> - contribution workflow and testing expectations.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/blob/main/SECURITY.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-primary hover:underline">SECURITY</a>
              <span> - private vulnerability reporting process.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-8">Frequently asked questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <details class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-gray-800 group">
            <summary class="px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">What is Moaiy?</h3>
              <span class="text-accent-primary text-2xl group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">+</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-4">
              <p class="font-body text-text-secondary">Moaiy is an open-source encryption project designed for practical OpenPGP-style workflows.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-gray-800 group">
            <summary class="px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">How can I download Moaiy safely?</h3>
              <span class="text-accent-primary text-2xl group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">+</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-4">
              <p class="font-body text-text-secondary">Use official GitHub Releases and validate checksums before running binaries.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-gray-800 group">
            <summary class="px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">Does Moaiy process plaintext on remote servers?</h3>
              <span class="text-accent-primary text-2xl group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">+</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-4">
              <p class="font-body text-text-secondary">Documentation and usage flows are local-first. Review the security page for current security model details.</p>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-bg-secondary to-bg-tertiary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6 text-center">Need a specific workflow?</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <a href="/encrypt-files-on-macos/" class="bg-bg-primary rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700 hover:border-accent-primary/50 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Encrypt files on macOS</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">Hands-on macOS guide for file protection.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/openpgp-made-simple/" class="bg-bg-primary rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700 hover:border-accent-primary/50 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">OpenPGP made simple</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">Concept guide for onboarding users.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/gpg-tools-alternative/" class="bg-bg-primary rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700 hover:border-accent-primary/50 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">GPG alternative view</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">Compare workflow complexity and fit.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
